{
  "stem": "25809.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It didn't satisfy me enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Higher-- higher [DUTCH] or higher professional--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--teaching?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, that must have been at that school, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Must have been at that because I was 14 when I went to-- 14 or 15 when I went there, yeah.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And yeah, in no time I had my own group, and I was running it like, oh,  we do this, we do this, we do this.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And hey, it was a-- it was an eight-piece group I had put together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Three girls-- no, two girls were singing and then five-- and four people playing music, It was six piece.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were rehearsing, and the music was bloody awful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we had a lot of fun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we started playing music left, right, and center, wherever I could, and I started playing my guitar after that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And by then, I'm about 17, and I started putting a band together with piano, drums, and myself guitar.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I put dance evenings together for Magen David, which was a Jewish club of youngsters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I convinced Rabbi Prins to let me have the upstairs room at the Lekstraat synagogue, where every Sunday at 7 o'clock all the kids would meet, and I was running the band.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Eventually, this became like the staple thing to do on a Sunday night for all the Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The band had no name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No,  the band had no name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the Hawaiian band had a name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was called the Golden Strings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later on when I worked professionally on Surfers Paradise, the-- the group I-- the three-piece group was called the-- the Flamingo Trio, because we were playing at the flamingo restaurant.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I was cranking out music, mediocre as it must have been.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But everybody was happy, and everybody was dancing.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
